For a scalable Motoko backend, don't build everything in one file. Structure it like a production trading or financial system.

**Full guides (reusable for any ICP project):**

- [motok/README.md](./motok/README.md) вЂ” documentation index
- [motok/code-guide.md](./motok/code-guide.md) вЂ” architecture, layers, feature workflow, migrations, tests
- [motok/deploy-guide.md](./motok/deploy-guide.md) вЂ” build, local, mainnet, upgrade, troubleshooting

